irgines devotae et monasticae,) <foreign xml:lang="gez">እለ፡ ውእቶን፡ መራዕዋተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</foreign> F.M. 6,10; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡ እማንቱ፡ ይኩና፡ መርዓውያቲሁ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Sx. Jac." loc="6">Sx. Jac. 6</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">መጋቤ፡ መራዕይ፡</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="grc">νυμφαγωγός</foreign> <ref cRef="Gen." loc="21,22">Gen. 21,22</ref>; <ref cRef="Gen." loc="26,26">Gen. 26,26</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኵሎሙ፡ ያረኵሱ፡ መራዕወ፡ ደቂቆሙ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Hez." loc="22,11">Hez. 22,11</ref>. 
